4.1 Core Performance Benchmarks

Metric Minimum Target Stretch Goal
Inference Speed (simple task) 10ms end-to-end 1ms
Learning Rate (new pattern) 10 examples 1 example
Energy per Inference 10mJ 1mJ
Simultaneous Tasks 100 10,000
Context Window 1 hour continuous 1 week continuous
Failure Rate <0.001% per day <0.0001% per day

4.2 Quality Metrics

· Cognitive Accuracy: 99.5% on standardized reasoning tests
· Adaptation Speed: <10 minutes for new environment optimization
· Creativity Index: >75% on Torrance Tests of Creative Thinking (adapted)
· Explainability: 95% of decisions with traceable reasoning chain
· Ethical Compliance: 100% adherence to programmed ethical constraints

4.3 Scalability Limits

· Maximum Edge Nodes: 1,000,000 per QUENNE instance
· Maximum Quantum Qubits: 10,000 logical (expandable via distributed QC)
· Maximum Memory: 10¹⁵ associative patterns (1 petapattern)
· Geographic Span: Global with <100ms maximum latency
· Administrative Domains: 1,000 independent but interoperable domains

