5. DEVELOPMENT ROADMAP

Phase 1: Foundation (12-18 months)

· QPU: 100-qubit processor with basic state inference
· Neuromorphic: 10⁶ neuron chip with STDP learning
· Edge: Basic sensor fusion on existing hardware
· Software: Simulation environment and basic APIs

Phase 2: Integration (24-30 months)

· QPU: 1,000-qubit with error correction
· Quantum-Neuro Interface: First functional prototype
· 6G Integration: Testbed with semantic signaling
· Applications: First vertical solutions (healthcare monitoring)

Phase 3: Maturity (36-48 months)

· Full Stack: All layers operational
· Scalability: 1,000-node deployment
· Autonomy: Level 4 autonomous operation in controlled environments
· Commercialization: First enterprise customers

Phase 4: Evolution (60+ months)

· Self-Improvement: Architecture can modify its own structure
· General Intelligence: Human-level performance on broad tasks
· Ecosystem: Third-party developers building on QUENNE platform

